00:20:23.350 --> 00:20:24.830
and then come inside and eat it.

00:20:24.830 --> 00:20:27.610
I know a lot of people
are doing more of that.

00:20:27.610 --> 00:20:29.980
It's such an easy
way to get basically

00:20:29.980 --> 00:20:33.365
free food and food that is
fresh and healthy all the time.

00:20:33.365 --> 00:20:35.240
You know exactly what's
gone into growing it.

00:20:35.240 --> 00:20:37.592
So, yeah, I highly
recommend it for everybody.

