00:21:12.670 --> 00:21:16.210
Almost exclusively, all
the animals in our diet--

00:21:16.210 --> 00:21:20.860
certainly here in the US and in
North America and in Europe--

00:21:20.860 --> 00:21:22.810
are animals that have
been bred specifically

00:21:22.810 --> 00:21:25.460
for the purpose of
industrial agriculture.

