00:22:46.540 --> 00:22:48.710
We're breeding them
specifically for this purpose.

00:22:48.710 --> 00:22:52.690
So when people eat less and
less and less animal products,

00:22:52.690 --> 00:22:55.700
we breed less and
less of the animals.

00:22:55.700 --> 00:22:58.270
